descriptionHTML:
The watch face with art nouveau style.

NOTE: Please make sure your watch is running Android Wear 5.0 or above.



Features on one face:
✔ 3D Parallax effect
✔ Wifi state
✔ Compass
✔ Weather
✔ Temperature
✔ Watch/phone battery level
✔ Step count
✔ Month, Date and Day
✔ Color picker for flower pattern
✔ Color picker for watch gear
✔ Color picker for weather
✔ Display in dimmed mode


Support all models:
✔ LG G Watch R
✔ Motorola Moto 360
✔ Samsung Gear Live
✔ Asus Zen Watch
✔ LG G watch
✔ Sony SmartWatch 3


Weather support:
http://openweathermap.org/


How to launch:
1. After install run 'Resync app' on Android Wear App.
2. Long press the watch screen and select Psychron from the watch face picker
3. You might need to wait a second before the app is synced for both phone and watch.
comments: So far, so nice Looks good, nice customization, battery, watch, and weather included, I really like the sophisticated look of it all. Five stars when I see how it does the battery..
